{"tid":2001914,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"李婉華去年9月有傳她在節目中播放《願榮光歸香港》因而被封咪","createTime":"2020-05-05T01:25:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T12:35:28.000Z","uid":351574,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3e0fe0068a7e97c37af3cbad6935721a71dd9a12","tid":2001914,"uid":351574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T01:25:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20200504/1588568497106/主持15年加國電台節目突結束-李婉華-好突然同難過\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20200504%2F1588568497106%2F%E4%B8%BB%E6%8C%8115%E5%B9%B4%E5%8A%A0%E5%9C%8B%E9%9B%BB%E5%8F%B0%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE%E7%AA%81%E7%B5%90%E6%9D%9F-%E6%9D%8E%E5%A9%89%E8%8F%AF-%E5%A5%BD%E7%AA%81%E7%84%B6%E5%90%8C%E9%9B%A3%E9%81%8E&d=QLsQNhMpkN58D9M0TNJg1mHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=8075ce5d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20200504%2F1588568497106%2F%E4%B8%BB%E6%8C%8115%E5%B9%B4%E5%8A%A0%E5%9C%8B%E9%9B%BB%E5%8F%B0%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE%E7%AA%81%E7%B5%90%E6%9D%9F-%E6%9D%8E%E5%A9%89%E8%8F%AF-%E5%A5%BD%E7%AA%81%E7%84%B6%E5%90%8C%E9%9B%A3%E9%81%8E&h=aa4a050c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20200504/1588568497106/主持15年加國電台節目突結束-李婉華-好突然同難過</a> <br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】李婉華早年移居加拿大，她為加拿大中文電台主持節目《小心華之里》，是電台受歡迎節目之一。去年香港的社會運動，李婉華一直很關心，9月她在節目中播放《願榮光歸香港》後，有傳電台收投訴要她「封咪」。後來李婉華工作如常，但日前突然接通知節目《小心華之里》結束，電台聲稱是「重整架構，靈活分享資源」，她原本周一至五的工作被刪減為一星期做一小時節目，疑被秋後算帳。<br />\n<br />\n李婉華在YouTube「住加女人」頻道回應該壞消息，向聽眾交代。她提到移民溫哥華10多年，照顧家庭及做電台節目，她說：「我好少同世界各地朋友接觸及互動，直至我播『榮光』首歌，得到好大迴響，好多傳聞，話我畀人『滅聲』，又話我無得做電台節目。」對主持了15年的節目被結束，她稱感突然與難過。她以後將更多精神與時間做好「住加女人」，希望大家支持。<br />\n李婉華接受《明報》訪問，她表示沒後悔節目中播《願榮光歸香港》，「感難過是電台沒有商量便突然cut節目，對老闆來說總有他們的理由，但對我而言，任何理由也是難以接受！我希望公司會珍惜員工」。<br />\n<br />\n「住加女人」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6eWD4HZH4tE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6eWD4HZH4tE&d=QLsQNhMpkN58D9M0TNJg1mHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=838c06a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6eWD4HZH4tE</a><br />\n<br />\n加拿大中文電台 Facebook- <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/am1470fm961/reviews/?referrer=page_recommendations_see_all&amp;ref=page_internal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2Fam1470fm961%2Freviews%2F%3Freferrer%3Dpage_recommendations_see_all%26ref%3Dpage_internal&d=QLsQNhMpkN58D9M0TNJg1mHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=1cf6737b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/am1470fm961/reviews/?referrer=page_recommendations_see_all&amp;ref=page_internal</a>"},{"pid":"458f44bfdf622a6513ced2ebc5003fa8b892fd71","tid":2001914,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T01:32:21.000Z","msg":"唔止佢，好多都 cut 人；好多電台都 cut 節目主持，分減工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a949ad83c57b5445b056bc34ab9e5fa531ae23","tid":2001914,"uid":184147,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T04:14:28.000Z","msg":"而家有直播睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5fda72a8e2b74ab0a061927e582a6f21aab2157","tid":2001914,"uid":151544,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T04:16:34.000Z","msg":"佢條channel 叫住家女人，去支持下"},{"pid":"b46df0541727fc3a7a6e8d42f2af1396df87a69a","tid":2001914,"uid":65024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5fda72a8e2b74ab0a061927e582a6f21aab2157","tid":2001914,"uid":151544,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T04:16:34.000Z","msg":"佢條channel 叫住家女人，去支持下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T12:35:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal